{"tid":2386334,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［自家廚房］港式羅宋湯","createTime":"2021-01-29T13:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T04:43:47.000Z","uid":132749,"like":97,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd369af03fb4e3f74649cfc0a9d5db3e471d40e","tid":2386334,"uid":132749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:38:20.000Z","msg":"今次整左個羅宋湯 ，整左勁大煲，有排飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6goWPRP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6goWPRP.jpg&h=ceff407c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n整宜個湯，最緊要燒左d牛肋骨先，唔好拎去出水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，出水同煲番茄薯仔湯咁，完全唔香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4dG0Xq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4dG0Xq.jpg&h=bf82f1fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n燒左差唔多一個鐘，乾身晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jRqaUiB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjRqaUiB.jpg&h=88725850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雜菜切粒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJXD3dD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJXD3dD.jpg&h=af97ec52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n切完就炒香d雜菜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2EyR68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2EyR68.jpg&h=0a7e423f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落大量茄膏再炒香佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BsWQUku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBsWQUku.jpg&h=663feb28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n炒完就可以扲去煲，煲3個鐘左右就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2iufk09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2iufk09.jpg&h=0f5c39eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A4pOF1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA4pOF1c.jpg&h=dbb84d15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛肉焗得夠，煲完出黎係同街食到既味一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8Z600Ii6j6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8Z600Ii6j6U&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=165d1b77\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8Z600Ii6j6U</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾意既記得subscribe, like 同share 我YouTube Channel,仲有follow 我ig <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=c257a82d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/channel/UCGJHwItoXY4IkZX7efJvCXg</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/openfridge_kitchendiary/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fopenfridge_kitchendiary%2F&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VHzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=59089881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/openfridge_kitchendiary/</a>"},{"pid":"6d15c3dc97fb2bfc8982726435bdf2b9ac11963e","tid":2386334,"uid":272819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:38:56.000Z","msg":"港宋好好飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}